You're correct, svgpathtools was choking on redundantly closed polygons.  This is fixed now.

I decided the desired behavior should be to have a k-pointed SVG-Polygon element become a k-Line Path object.  This way information encoded as a k-pointed polygon is preserved in the transformation to a path object.

